<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">不过话说回来，<delay40 />
<anim id="Sighing" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" />你这家伙无论何时<delay8 />都是一副
我行我素、<delay8 />不紧不慢的样子啊！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="QuestionMark" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" />诶～？<delay20 />你说什么呀～？<delay40 />
<anim id="Blushing" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" />被人用那么复杂的词夸了，
还真是让人害羞啊～<tag a="110" b="6" />。<anim id="EmotEnd" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Worried" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" />唉<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay40 />
你总是这副样子，<delay8 />
让我不禁有些担心。<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /><anim id="Thinking" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" />比如说，我想想<tag a="110" b="0" /><10_4 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" />你没有什么梦想吗？<delay20 />
比如将来想变成什么样之类的。</message>
	<message label="004" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" />啊！<delay20 />梦想～？！<delay40 />
有啊、有啊～！<delay20 />我想想<tag a="110" b="0" /></message>
	<message label="005" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" />比如说～<delay20 />
在一个很大的脸盆里
装满<tag a="135" b="1" arg="0xcd00" /><anim id="Shocked" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="0" /><20_2 arg="3" />
<anim id="HappyFlower" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" />然后把脸浸没进去，<delay20 />
看看自己<delay20 />
可以屏多久的气～<20_2 arg="4" /><anim id="Oops" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" />
最后把自己的名字写进
专门保存各种世界纪录的书里，<delay20 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" />这就是我的梦想～<anim id="OhGeez" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" />
<tag a="110" b="0" /><anim id="Shocked" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" />啊！<delay20 />不过吧～<delay8 />
<anim id="Blushing" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" />我挑战到一半，肯定会忍住不住
喝掉盆里的饮料，<delay8 />这样不行吧～<delay20 /><tag a="110" b="6" />。<anim id="Smiling" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="006" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Outraged" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" />谁管你啊！<delay40 />
<anim id="Angry" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" />随你便吧！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="007" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我想用我最喜欢的<delay8 /><tag a="135" b="7" arg="0xcd00" /><delay8 />
来造一座房子～！<anim id="Shocked" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /><pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />房间里的家具也要用甜点来制作，<delay8 />
造一座真正的甜点小屋～<delay20 />
<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />嘻嘻～<delay8 />听上去很好吃吧～？
<anim id="Aha" target="actor" targetSpec="" />啊！<delay8 />不过，<delay8 />
用甜点造的房子，
<anim id="Frantic" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我一定忍不住<delay8 />会去吃的<tag a="110" b="0" /><anim id="OhGeez" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" />
<anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />然后就变成了一座到处是洞的房子，<delay8 />
这会让我<delay8 />很困扰的，<delay20 />
怎么办才好呀～？！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="008" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我的梦想就是，<delay8 />在一个刚好够装
<anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我一个人的篮子上<delay8 />绑满气球～<pageBreak /><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />嘻嘻～然后就坐着它<delay8 />
<anim id="Love" target="actor" targetSpec="" />飞上天空玩～！<delay20 />
一定<delay8 />会很有趣的～
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但是，<delay8 /><anim id="Frantic" target="actor" targetSpec="" />万一飞到很远的地方去了，
我该怎么办呀～？！<delay40 /><anim id="Sighing" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" />
我还能<delay8 />回得来吗～</message>
	<message label="009" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Angry" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我担心的<delay8 />
就是你这种个性啊！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="010" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我想成为发明家，<delay8 />
然后<delay8 />发明出一种<delay8 />
<anim id="Love" target="actor" targetSpec="" />怎么吃都不会少的<tag a="135" b="3" arg="0xcd00" />～<anim id="Shocked" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="4" />、<tag a="110" b="31" arg="0xcd00" /><tag a="110" b="13" />，<delay8 />
我也会分给
你们俩的，<delay8 /><anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />放心吧～<anim id="ShyBoy" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" />
<anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不过，<delay8 />到底应该
怎么发明呢～？<delay20 />
唔……<delay8 />唔<tag a="110" b="0" />
<anim id="Sleepy" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="0" /><tag a="110" b="0" /><anim id="Aha" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" />
想着想着，<delay8 />
好像有点困了呢～<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="011" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />等我长大了，<delay8 />
我想开一家<delay8 />
刨冰专卖店～！
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />虽然我不太喜欢<delay8 />
<anim id="Shaking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />吃刨冰的时候<delay8 />头疼的感觉，
<anim id="HappyFlower" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但是冰冰绵绵的口感，<delay8 />非常好吃呢～<anim id="Nodding" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />如果我自己开了刨冰店，<delay8 />
我就能每天吃刨冰了吧～？<anim id="Eh" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /><pageBreak /><anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />所以，我想要开一家<delay8 /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />
属于自己的刨冰店呢～<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="013" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你要是自己吃掉了，
还开什么刨冰店啊<tag a="110" b="0" /><tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="101" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Silent" target="actor" targetSpec="" />听好咯！<delay40 />
我今天就破例教你一些<delay8 />
比较有气势的台词吧。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="102" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Eh" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你要教我
有气势的台词～？<delay20 />
<anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我想学～<delay8 />我想学～！</message>
	<message label="103" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />如果有人在你面前说些不知所云的话，
这时你就直接回对方一句<delay20 />
“你说啥啊”！<pageBreak /><anim id="Silent" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你说啥啊！<delay8 />
你这个大笨蛋！<delay20 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="0" />来吧，<delay8 />你也学着说说看。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="104" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Confused" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你、<delay8 />你说啥呀～！<delay20 />
大笨蛋～！<delay20 />
<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="0" />是像这样吗～？</message>
	<message label="105" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />嗯……<delay8 />还有待提高啊。<delay20 />
不过，<delay8 /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />也算是离成为豪爽的男子汉
更近了一步吧？</message>
	<message label="106" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />太好了～！<delay20 /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />
我也要变得像<tag a="110" b="31" arg="0xcd00" /><tag a="110" b="13" /><delay8 />
一样帅气～！<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />话说回来<tag a="110" b="0" />
<anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你说的“大笨蛋”是谁啊～？<anim id="Oops" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="107" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />要是有人在你面前说蠢话，<delay8 />
你就直接回一句<delay8 />“糊涂虫！”就好啦！<pageBreak /><anim id="Silent" target="actor" targetSpec="" />糊涂虫！<delay8 />
你这个大笨蛋！<delay20 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="0" />来吧，<delay8 />你也学着说说看。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="108" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Confused" target="actor" targetSpec="" />糊、<delay8 />糊涂虫～！<delay20 />
你这个大笨蛋～！<delay20 />
<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="0" />是像这样吗～？</message>
	<message label="109" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />要是有人在你面前说些不着边际的话，<delay20 />
你就直接回一句<delay8 />“赶紧走开！”就好啦！<pageBreak /><anim id="Silent" target="actor" targetSpec="" />赶紧走开！<delay8 />
你这个大笨蛋！<delay20 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="0" />来吧，<delay8 />你也学着说说看。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="110" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Confused" target="actor" targetSpec="" />赶、<delay8 />赶紧走开～！<delay20 />
你这个大笨蛋～！<delay20 />
<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="0" />是像这样吗～？</message>
	<message label="201" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Sleepy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />呼<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="40" />
总觉得今天特别困，<delay8 />
提不起干劲啊。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="202" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Sleepy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />哈——欠<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="40" />
我也被<delay8 /><tag a="110" b="31" arg="0xcd00" /><tag a="110" b="13" />带得
打起了哈欠呢～<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="203" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="WrySmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />喂，<delay20 />
连我的口头禅<delay8 />
都传染给你啦！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="204" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Shocked" target="actor" targetSpec="" />诶～？！<delay20 />
我完全没发现呢～<delay20 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不过，<delay8 />“<tag a="110" b="5" />”真好听～<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />话说～<delay20 />
从现在开始，“<tag a="110" b="5" />”这个口头禅
<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />能不能也给我用用呀～？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="205" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你现在才问能不能<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
这不是<delay8 />都已经用起来了吗！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />算了，<delay8 />随你喜欢吧！</message>
